cho_description:
Forehead, ears, and modius crown with cobra frieze, of a granodiorite statue of Sekhmet. British Museum object EA90784. 

COL: http://www.britishmuseum.org/research/collection_online/collection_object_details.aspx?objectId=3764105&partId=1

Draft model by Jennifer Wexler, using 39 photos, with the reverse to be done in the future.
